embeds.title: Cryo Chamber
embeds.description:
Rare Relic / The Guardian / Downfall

At the start of each combat, gain 1 Stasis slot. Whenever a card enters **Stasis,** **Upgrade** it.
*Things always seem better coming out than they did going in.*

messages.content: Yeah with cryo chamber it looks better
its guardian tho
put it in stasis once then its a retaining 0 cost brace 10
Yeah true
with cryo chamber it's 0 cost 15

You can always bottle an apotheosis (very powerful with holy water). You can also use stasis, especially future plans to help reduce the cost. Really not sure how strong this will be, it makes it easier to get into your first defensive mode, but doesn't give you that instant 20 block. The main interaction to watch out for will be with curl up, which can both get you the last 10 brace you need, and place gear up into stasis for you to make it cheaper to play. Upgrading curl up and the first campfire will let you guarantee that cost reduction as well, and you almost never had a reason to upgrade curl up early. I can also imagine plenty of turns where you aren't getting attacked and afford to spend 1 energy to get you closer to defensive mode. Will need to play with this a bit to get a better feel.
